OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain at times, mainly
OL,7,Facross the North Pennines and
OL,8,FCheviots. Drier to the east of the
OL,9,FPennines with occasional cloud breaks.
OL,10,FBreezy and mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FCloudy with outbreaks of
OL,13,Frain across western hills becoming
OL,14,Fheavier and more persistent through
OL,15,FThursday, before easing for a time in
OL,16,Fthe evening. Drier in the east. Rather
OL,17,Fwindy, mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
